# Dar-Ul-Quran — Cline Rules

## Project

Next.js 16 App Router + React 19 + Sanity v6 CMS + Tailwind CSS v4.
Islamic educational website, fully RTL (Urdu/Arabic), TypeScript strict mode.

---

## Commands

```bash
npm run dev     # Dev server → localhost:3001 (see deploy/runtime.cjs)
npm run build   # Production build
npm run start   # Production server → 0.0.0.0:3001
npm run lint    # ESLint check
```

Studio: http://localhost:3001/studio

---

## Rules

### Server vs Client Components
- Default: Server Component (no directive needed)
- Add `"use client"` ONLY for: useState, useEffect, event handlers, browser APIs
- Never import sanity client or nodemailer in client components

### Data Fetching
- All GROQ queries → `sanity/lib/queries.ts` (never inline)
- Always use `safeFetch` from `sanity/lib/client.ts` (null-safe)
- No `useEffect` for data — use async Server Components
- ISR: `export const revalidate = 300` on CMS-backed pages

### Navigation & Images
- `<Link>` from `next/link` — never raw `<a>`
- `<Image>` from `next/image` — never raw `<img>`

### TypeScript
- No `any`. No `@ts-ignore` without a comment.
- `type` keyword for props, not `interface`
- Strict mode always on

### Tailwind v4
- PostCSS plugin mode (`@tailwindcss/postcss`)
- Brand: `dq-600`/`dq-700` (gold) as primary colors
- Spacing: `ms-*`/`me-*` for RTL-safe inline spacing
- Opacity: `bg-black/50` syntax (not `bg-opacity-*`)
- No `styled-components`, `emotion`, or CSS-in-JS

### RTL / Urdu
- Root: `lang="ur" dir="rtl"` — never override without reason
- Body text: `leading-[1.8]` minimum
- Use `rtl:` Tailwind prefix for directional overrides

### CMS Content
- Never hardcode phone, email, social links — always from Sanity `siteSettings`
- `seo { title, description }` on every content type query
- Slug field required on all public document types

### Code Quality
- No `console.log` in committed code
- No raw hex for brand colors — use `dq-*` tokens
- No abbreviations in Urdu/Arabic string constants

---

## Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `sanity/lib/queries.ts` | All GROQ queries |
| `sanity/lib/client.ts` | Sanity client + safeFetch |
| `tailwind.config.ts` | Design tokens |
| `app/globals.css` | Keyframes + base styles |
| `components/ui/Reveal.tsx` | Scroll animations |

---

## Environment Variables

`NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_PROJECT_ID`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_DATASET`, `SANITY_API_TOKEN`, `EMAIL_USER`, `EMAIL_PASS`, `EMAIL_TO`
Never commit these. Never log these.
